last_episode_to_air.name: Don't Shoot!
last_episode_to_air.overview: In Newaygo County, Mich., Marty and Glenna Duram are found gunned down in their home; investigators find evidence of a troubled marriage at the heart of this crime as well as a pet parrot that repeats Marty's last words.

name: Til Death Do Us Part
overview: Investigative series that chronicles the relationships of couples that end with a fatal destiny.
